{
  "title": "ReFi Roundup #24: Plastiks.io wins Celo Camp, Impact DAO research, ETH Barcelona & Spirals Protocol reveal",
  "slug": "refi-roundup-24",
  "html": "<h2 id=\"plastiksio-nft-marketplace-takes-gold-prize-at-celo-camp-2022-%E2%99%BB%EF%B8%8F\">Plastiks.io NFT Marketplace takes Gold Prize at Celo Camp 2022! â™»ï¸</h2><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/07/image-7.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1400\" height=\"948\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/07/image-7.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/07/image-7.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/07/image-7.png 1400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>The team at Plastiks.io have built the first NFT marketplace that fights plastic pollutionâ€”and they've won Gold Prize at <a href=\"https://medium.com/celoorg/announcing-the-grand-prize-winners-and-awardees-of-celo-camp-batch-5-cfccfcc2a3fb\">Celo Camp 2022</a> which earned them. 10,000 cUSD and 2,000 CELO.</p><p>We also caught a glimpse of their talk at ETH Barcelona, which earned their founder and CEO Andre a ReFi Orb. He's definitely worth a follow!</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/AndreVanyiRobin?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@AndreVanyiRobin</a> enjoyed your talk about <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Plastiks_io?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@Plastiks_io</a> at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/eth_barcelona?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@eth_barcelona</a>...<a href=\"https://t.co/MWZHjE7xBj\">https://t.co/MWZHjE7xBj</a><br><br>Welcome to <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a> ser! <br><br>Great to build alongside you. ğŸ™ğŸ¼ <a href=\"https://t.co/n1GBqsEgEO\">pic.twitter.com/n1GBqsEgEO</a></p>&mdash; jE â¤ï¸ MRV ğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¦ (@climateXcrypto) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/climateXcrypto/status/1545353301163745280?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">July 8, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><hr><h2 id=\"gitcoin-funding-takes-us-forward-%F0%9F%91%8F\">Gitcoin funding takes us forward ğŸ‘</h2><p>The bear market has given many of us time to slow down and prepare. Despite the market conditions, regens are still actively funding public goods in record scale with over $5M committed to hundreds of projects across Gitcoin GR14. Four of the top 5 funded projects were from the ReFi community!</p><p>We're super grateful to have been near the top of the list alongside such brilliant builders.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/07/image-6.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"836\" height=\"1024\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/07/image-6.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/07/image-6.png 836w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://gitcoin.co/blog/gr14-results/\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">View full results</a></div><hr><h2 id=\"refi-at-eth-barcelona-%F0%9F%8C%99\">ReFi at ETH Barcelona ğŸŒ™</h2><p>Today marks the final day of ETH Barcelona, Spain's first Ethereum conference. It's a conference exploring how blockchain can help build a sustainable world full of human potential. With so many Regens across carbon, ecosystems and social justice this is worth taking a glimpse into the live streams with incredible speakers from <a href=\"https://toucan.earth/\">Toucan</a>, <a href=\"https://foresight.org/\">Foresight Institute</a>, and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/cryptodrftng\">Ukraine DAO</a>.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">ğŸŒ™GOOD NIGHTğŸŒ™<br>Day two of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ETHBarcelona?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ETHBarcelona</a> was incredibleğŸ‘©â€ğŸš€ğŸš€<br>See you tomorrow. <a href=\"https://t.co/KMVuJPvXFI\">pic.twitter.com/KMVuJPvXFI</a></p>&mdash; ETHBarcelona (@eth_barcelona) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/eth_barcelona/status/1545158249971843072?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">July 7, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h3 id=\"eth-bcn-sky-stage-live-stream\">ETH BCN Sky Stage Live Stream</h3><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/h_fxdJrpwy0?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen title=\"Eth BCN - Sky Stage - day3\"></iframe></figure><h3 id=\"eth-bcn-forest-stage-live-stream\">ETH BCN Forest Stage Live Stream</h3><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/yoWn-hDG7-Y?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen title=\"ETH BCN - Forest stage - Day 3\"></iframe></figure><hr><h2 id=\"spirals-protocol-says-hello-%F0%9F%91%8B\">Spirals Protocol says hello ğŸ‘‹</h2><p>We come across a lot of brilliant founders in our community at ReFi DAO but Helena Merk from Spirals Protocol has definitely caught our eye. ğŸ‘€</p><p>She and her team have a strong pedigree with previous exits and a clear vision for the future. Spirals is embedding regeneration into the fabric of Proof of Stake, their protocol is worth digging into as it could be a major unlock for the ReFi movement as the competition for planet positive layer ones continues to accelerate.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Hey ğŸ‘‹ We&#39;re Spirals, building a protocol to weave regenerative infrastructure directly into any proof of stake blockchain.<br><br>Any individual or DAO can choose to stake with validators running Spirals, turning their staking token balance into a climate impact funding machine! â›°ï¸</p>&mdash; Spirals Protocol ğŸŒ±ğŸ™ˆ (@SpiralsProtocol) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SpiralsProtocol/status/1544448711983390720?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">July 5, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h3 id=\"tune-in-%F0%9F%93%BB\">Tune in ğŸ“»</h3><p>Next Thursday at 1pm PT there's a Zoom webinar with Web3 Crypto Startups interviewing Helena about her work at Spirals protocol.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">âš¡ï¸New to ReFi?âš¡ï¸<br><br>Donâ€™t miss the opportunity to hear from <a href=\"https://twitter.com/HelenaMerk?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@HelenaMerk</a> how <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SpiralsProtocol?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@SpiralsProtocol</a> is turning crypto into an into a force for climate impactğŸŒ±ğŸŒ<br><br>Thursday, July 14 at 1pm PTğŸ˜<br><br>Register here ğŸ‘‰ <a href=\"https://t.co/bbHp2Ix8ra\">https://t.co/bbHp2Ix8ra</a></p>&mdash; Web3 Crypto Startups (@sf_meetup) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/sf_meetup/status/1544753689667063808?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">July 6, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p>Give <a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/HelenaMerk\">Helena</a> and <a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/spiralsprotocol\">her team</a> a follow and stay tuned for Spirals <a href=\"https://medium.com/celoorg/announcing-the-grand-prize-winners-and-awardees-of-celo-camp-batch-5-cfccfcc2a3fb\">upcoming launch on Celo.</a></p><hr><h1 id=\"owocki-on-refi-in-forbes-%F0%9F%91%8F\"><strong>Owocki on ReFi in Forbes ğŸ‘</strong></h1><p>Great to see Kevin's Greenpilled narrative taking foot in mainstream media. Check out the interview and article below!</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/lebtcGRnxTU?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen title=\"Can DAOs can build a green future? Kevin Owocki interview\"></iframe></figure><blockquote>What if we could use blockchain technology to create more coordination and solve coordination failures?</blockquote><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.forbes.com/sites/kylewestaway/2022/06/16/how-crypto-can-regenerate-the-world/\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Read more</a></div><hr><p>Alex Filotimo from Web3 Climate gives us an overview of his take on Kevin's book <a href=\"https://store.gitcoin.co/products/green-pill-book-digital-edition\">Greenpilled available on Gitcoin</a>...</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">I finally finished <a href=\"https://twitter.com/owocki?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@owocki</a>&#39;s Greenpill book! It is a beautiful reference point for crypto&#39;s future potential. <br><br>ğŸ›°ï¸ Coordination is one of this century&#39;s most important fields.<br><br>Building on that, here are my favorite notes:</p>&mdash; Alex Filotimo (@AFilotimo) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/AFilotimo/status/1541900418783088640?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 28, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><hr><h1 id=\"40-learnings-on-40-days-of-building-a-dao-%F0%9F%93%9A\">40 Learnings on 40 Days of Building a DAO ğŸ“š</h1><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/07/image-8.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1456\" height=\"1092\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/07/image-8.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/07/image-8.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/07/image-8.png 1456w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>A study of Impact DAOs from Deepa at Crypto Good</figcaption></figure><p>Our friend Deepa shares insights on her <a href=\"https://cryptogood.substack.com/p/-call-for-contributors-a-study-of\" rel>study of Impact DAOs</a> at their 40-day milestone. Her mission is to conduct an intensive study of DAOs that we will distill and publish as a free book and a series of podcasts and blog posts. These are some of Deepa's early learnings and on how to create a \"distributed autonomous organization\" or DAO from scratch.</p><p>Here are some snippets from her learnings:</p><blockquote>DAOs do need a leader initially that galvanizes the team and sets the course. But once the initial workâ€™s done new leaders emerge.</blockquote><blockquote>Be on Discord everyday even if it's just for 20 mins.</blockquote><blockquote>Shine the light on all active contributors - promote them, give them credit internally and on social.</blockquote><blockquote>DAOs need self driven folks with entrepreneurial mindset who seek solutions rather than problems.</blockquote><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://cryptogood.substack.com/p/learnings-on-building-a-dao-from\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Read more</a></div><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-08-at-11.47.04.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1898\" height=\"670\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-08-at-11.47.04.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-08-at-11.47.04.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-08-at-11.47.04.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-08-at-11.47.04.png 1898w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h2 id=\"decarbonized-24-improving-quality-of-carbon-credit-demand-soil-carbon-finding-scale-in-the-vcm\">deCarbonized #24: Improving quality of carbon credit demand; Soil carbon finding scale in the VCM</h2><p>Every week Dr. Anna Watson gives us an overview of the evolving voluntary carbon market across crypto and beyond. Here are some highlights of the stories in the 24th issue.</p><ul><li>ğŸŒ¾ Historic number of soil carbon credits enter the VCM via <a href=\"https://www.indigoag.com/pages/news/inaugural-carbon-by-indigo-credit-issuance\">Indigo Agriculture</a></li><li>ğŸ˜± Frontier's <a href=\"https://www.protocol.com/bulletins/frontier-cdr-purchases-stripe-alphabet?utm_campaign=RebelMouse&amp;share_id=7117860&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_content=Protocol\" rel=\"noopener\">six big tech companies</a> spent the first part of its $925 M advance commitment purchase </li><li>ğŸª¸World's first blockchain-based algae biomass project <a href=\"https://www.prnewswire.co.uk/news-releases/asset-backed-token-raise-to-support-the-build-of-algae-biomass-protein-farms-831288181.html\">announced</a> by <a href=\"https://sustainableimpacttokens.com/\">Sustainable Impact Token (STI) </a>on Tezos</li></ul><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blog.toucan.earth/decarbonized-24-improving-quality-of-demand-for-carbon-credits-soil-carbon-finding-scale-in-the-vcm/\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Read more</a></div><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-dark\" style=\"\" data-kg-background-image=\"\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-talent\">ReFi Talent</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"onboarding-the-best-talent-into-top-refi-ventures\">Onboarding the best talent into top ReFi ventures</h3></div><p>This week we've seen two entrepreneurs join the ReFi Talent collective, both of whom have received positive referrals from their previous employer at Solid World DAO. If you're growing your team, definitely reach out to <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Bati_ReFi\">Bhavesh</a> or <a href=\"https://twitter.com/0xClimate\">Priyank</a> or apply to join our Talent Collective and we can make an intro.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/07/image-9.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1412\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/07/image-9.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/07/image-9.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/07/image-9.png 1412w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-08-at-11.59.07.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1460\" height=\"644\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-08-at-11.59.07.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-08-at-11.59.07.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-08-at-11.59.07.png 1460w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-accent\" style=\"\" data-kg-background-image=\"\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-bites\">ReFi Bites</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"a-sampling-of-the-best-of-refi-twitter-and-beyond\">A sampling of the best of ReFi twitter and beyond...</h3></div><h2 id=\"eden-dao-launches-an-ultra-sound-money-carbon-footprint-calculator-alongside-the-eden-pledge\">Eden Dao launches an ultra-sound money carbon footprint calculator alongside the Eden pledge</h2><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/cyrusofeden\">Cyrus of Eden Dao</a> is a brilliant builder who has just released a prototype of a carbon footprint calculator which takes users to a pledge to join Eden Dao. Several early adopters have been testing it out and minting pledges for a regenerative future.</p><p>It'd be great to see the Ethereum community rally around offsetting the footprint of Proof of Work in the lead up to the merge!</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-08-at-10.42.11.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"664\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-08-at-10.42.11.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-08-at-10.42.11.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-08-at-10.42.11.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w2400/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-08-at-10.42.11.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-08-at-11.05.49.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1978\" height=\"770\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-08-at-11.05.49.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-08-at-11.05.49.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-08-at-11.05.49.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2022/07/Screenshot-2022-07-08-at-11.05.49.png 1978w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><hr><h2 id=\"10k-bounty-for-sustainable-blockchain-hackathon\">$10K Bounty for Sustainable Blockchain Hackathon</h2><p>In the lead up to Sustainable Blockchain Summit after ETH CC, our friends at HBAR have committed a $10k bounty for the best ReFi and sustainability project on Hedera. If you're considering building in this ecosystem the upcoming <a href=\"https://gitcoin.co/hackathon/sustainable/onboard\">Sustainable Blockchain Hackathon</a> hosted by Gitcoin is running June 23 - July 18, 2022, take a look!</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card kg-card-hascaption\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">ğŸ’°ğŸš¨ $10k Bounty for the &quot;Best ReFi &amp; Sustainability Project On <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hedera?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@hedera</a> up as part of the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Filecoin?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@Filecoin</a> Sustainable Blockchain Hackathon sponsored by the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/HBAR_foundation?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@HBAR_foundation</a>. For more info: <a href=\"https://t.co/66shrnPDOL\">https://t.co/66shrnPDOL</a></p>&mdash; Wes Geisenberger (@geisenbergerwes) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/geisenbergerwes/status/1544785329504358400?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">July 6, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n<figcaption>-</figcaption></figure><h2 id=\"reddit-launches-nft-marketplace-on-polygon\">Reddit launches NFT marketplace on Polygon</h2><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">GM <a href=\"https://twitter.com/0xPolygon?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@0xPolygon</a> Fam!<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Reddit?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@Reddit</a> is launching its NFT Marketplace on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/0xPolygon?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@0xPolygon</a>!<br><br>Goal : <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Top3?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Top3</a> by impact - BTC,ETH, Polygon; nothing less, nothing more. <br><br>Never stop building! WAGMI!<a href=\"https://t.co/VhSMEl2wJd\">https://t.co/VhSMEl2wJd</a></p>&mdash; Sandeep | Polygon ğŸ’œğŸ”3ï¸âƒ£ (@sandeepnailwal) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/sandeepnailwal/status/1545031787138654208?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">July 7, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><hr><h2 id=\"petroleum-engineers-going-extinct-%F0%9F%9B%A2%F0%9F%A6%A3\">Petroleum engineers going extinct ğŸ›¢ğŸ¦£</h2><p>Probably not for a while, but at least a lot less young people are choosing this career path.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">If you want a glimpse into the future of oil look at college enrollment rates for petroleum engineers <br><br>The kids know which way the wind is blowing <a href=\"https://t.co/cl5pKzOqXe\">pic.twitter.com/cl5pKzOqXe</a></p>&mdash; Justin Guay (@Guay_JG) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Guay_JG/status/1545005144726769665?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">July 7, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><hr><h2 id=\"regenerative-intelligence\">Regenerative Intelligence</h2><p>Chad Frischmann, one of the co-founders of Project Drawdown, had stepped down to start a new venture called Regenerative Intelligence to build:</p><p>a network of world class system thinkers and doers creating a virtuous cycle of collaborative intelligence, we enable the effective implementation of the highest impact â€˜system of solutionsâ€™ for the planet and for people at scale.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">NEWS: I am announcing not only my departure from <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ProjectDrawdown?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ProjectDrawdown</a> after 8 fantastic years but also the beginning of my new mission, Regenerative Intelligence.<br><br>Last week we released the latest updates to the climate solutions that can together stop global warming.ğŸ‘‡ <a href=\"https://t.co/RzqncKjTR4\">pic.twitter.com/RzqncKjTR4</a></p>&mdash; Chad Frischmann ğŸ³ï¸â€ğŸŒˆ (@ChadFrischmann) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ChadFrischmann/status/1545075322990649344?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">July 7, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><hr><h2 id=\"low-carbon-concrete-making-it-mainstream\">Low-carbon concrete making it mainstream</h2><p>Great to see major players adopting low-carbon concrete as an alternative for one of the most energy intensive building products that makes up a significant portion of the building industry's footprint